mcp-bible — data sources, licenses, and attribution
====================================================

The mcp-bible CODE is licensed MIT (see LICENSE). The bundled/derived BIBLE DATA
comes from the public sources below, each under its own license. Attribution and
usage obligations are preserved here as required.

The single distributable database (`data/bible.sqlite`) and the semantic-embedding
files (`data/embeddings/*.bin`) are DERIVED from these sources and are published as
GitHub Release assets (not committed to git). Every source below is public-domain or
openly licensed, so the derived DB is redistributable; the obligations (attribution,
no-text-alteration) carry through.

