SEMANTIC EMBEDDINGS
--------------------------------------------------------------------

Embedding model: BAAI/bge-m3 (https://huggingface.co/BAAI/bge-m3), MIT license,
served at query/build time via DeepInfra's OpenAI-compatible endpoint.
Precomputed vectors in data/embeddings/*.bin are derived from the public texts above.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
EXCLUDED
--------------------------------------------------------------------

SBLGNT (SBL Greek New Testament) is NOT bundled. Although the SBLGNT text is offered
under CC BY 4.0, its older EULA carries a restriction on Greek–English diglot/interlinear
distribution; to stay unambiguous, mcp-bible omits it. The Berean Greek NT (CC0) is used
instead. If a critical-text comparison is ever needed, it should be added as a separate
user-selected module, not bundled here.
